title: Roger Marshall
deleted: In 2017, Marshall's son, Cal, became a viral [[internet meme]] when he dabbed in front of then [[Speaker of the United States House of Representatives|Speaker of The House]], [[Paul Ryan]], during his father's Congressional Inauguration.<ref>{{Cite news|last=McCann|first=Erin|date=2017-01-04|title=Yes, a Teenager Dabbed in Front of Paul Ryan|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/04/us/politics/dabbing-paul-ryan-cal-marshall.html|access-date=2021-09-27|issn=0362-4331}}</ref> Marshall joked on [[Twitter]] that his son was grounded.<ref>{{Cite web|title=https://twitter.com/rogermarshallmd/status/816402331143118848|url=https://twitter.com/rogermarshallmd/status/816402331143118848|access-date=2021-09-27|website=Twitter|language=en}}</ref>
